

	 
      it smells so good and it is so soft that i love it. it is so sweet like chocolate covered strawberry shortcake. that is the sweetest best cake ever. it has a similar effect to mixing ornette coleman with simon and garfunkel. dark sweet mellow beautifully patterned chaos. splashes of red. vibrant sparkling. light laughter throughout. bubbling energy that has an inordinate fullness. insatiable consumption.   the silence between sleeps is divine and sweet in its own. but nothing is better than being in bed. dream states. waking and trailing whispy thoughts. like smoke from a brilliantly burning candle.  blown about by fluttering fans.  
     
    
